---
title: Grilled Beef & Charred Baby Broccoli Salad with Balsamic Glaze
description: Turn up the heat with our latest barbecue creation! Juicy, flame-kissed beef rump brings smokey flavours, while charred baby broccoli adds a vibrant contrast. Tossed with fresh greens and a melted garlic-spiked butter, it’s a hearty salad that celebrates the best of outdoor grilling flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6735a33217ac05644df7d3f6-0b19dd17.jpeg
